{"tid":1134941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳所羅門群島與台灣斷交　蔡英文：努力穩固邦交國","createTime":"2019-05-02T04:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T04:54:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9f1dc0ad159c573ef1fdf5db74a02d48f67701","tid":1134941,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190502/s00004/a00de254ee40ebba93f5542f182fd90a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190502%2Fs00004%2Fa00de254ee40ebba93f5542f182fd90a.jpg&h=71d8ccec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣17個邦交國之一所羅門群島，傳出會與台灣斷交。台灣總統蔡英文稱，會在外交上努力穩固邦交國。<br />\n<br />\n《澳洲人報》昨日（1日）報道，所羅門群島總理蘇嘉瓦瑞（Manasseh Sogavare）接受當地傳媒訪問時表示，目前與台灣狀態不變，但外交關係會持續發展，原則是考慮所羅門群島如何從中獲得利益。<br />\n<br />\n台灣總統蔡英文今日（2日）稱，掌握整個情況，會在外交上努力穩固邦交國。台灣外交部發言人李憲章表示，將持續與所羅門群島政府在既有合作基礎上，開拓更多合作空間，落實「踏實外交、互利互惠」精神，促進區域穩定、和平與繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸是所羅門群島最大貿易伙伴，與其他太平洋島國如帕勞、吉里巴斯等一樣，所羅門群島與台灣有邦交關係。"},{"pid":"17977b0da816d2836500b23b77bff02f60bbd4c4","tid":1134941,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190502/s00004/1556764864577/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190502%2Fs00004%2F1556764864577%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmeaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=a722c08a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190502%2Fs00004%2F1556764864577%2F&h=b5cc480c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190502/s00004/1556764864577/</a>"},{"pid":"9459e01218d221f4a243dfd116f133c433f42a5a","tid":1134941,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:22:30.000Z","msg":"講到底都係錢，又玩債務外交"},{"pid":"185c8014e59a38bd97b84b24f0be17dcc339e251","tid":1134941,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"d 邦交早廿年就有用  係聯合國多d票<br />\n<br />\n而家傾真係續單計   邦唔邦交都一樣"}]}